Fullish delivery in the channel outside the offstump, angling away and Smith, the last hope for West Indies, pushed at it, got an edge and Hadding pouched it with glee. Bracken turns to appeal, gets the nod he was looking for, turns, and runs over to his teammates to join in the celebratory huddle.

commentPostTextItems.html: West Indies were, it appeared, coasting after a frenzied and flamboyant calypso start given by Chanderpaul and Gayle but soon after that the never-say-die spirit and the professionalism of Australia was on show. They stormed their way back into the game, helped along by some batsmen spontaneously combusting  in the middle, and in the end have won by a deceptively massive 78 run-margin.
This is Sriram Veera, signing off. Catch you on the 14th for the India v West Indies match. Till then, Good bye and good luck.
